monero.wallet.request

Class MoneroTxRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • monero.daemon.model.MoneroTx
      • monero.wallet.model.MoneroTxWallet
        • monero.wallet.request.MoneroTxRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Filter<MoneroTxWallet>

    public class MoneroTxRequest
extends MoneroTxWallet
implements Filter<MoneroTxWallet>
    Configures a request to retrieve transactions. All transactions are returned except those that do not meet the criteria defined in this request.
